Default constructor. Creates an entity with id -1 meaning that it is not stored in the database.

Contractor

public Contractor(java.lang.String[] array,
                  long id)
Constructor that creates an entity with data given as String array. This is a convenience method of wrapping database records retrieved from lower level database API returning records as String[]. Order of elements in the array will map properties as follows: [name, location, specialities, size, rate, owner].

public java.lang.String[] toArray()
